    "slug": "2026-05-17-overbrook-high-school-facilities-master-plan",
    "title": "Overbrook High School and the politics of school buildings",
    "publishedAt": "2026-05-17",
    "excerpt": "Overbrook’s legends weren’t just made in a gym—they were made in a public institution. Philadelphia’s 2026 facilities master plan asks a hard civic question: what do we owe the neighborhood schools that create our shared life?",
    "tags": [],
    "heroImage": "/assets/blog/overbrook-high-school-facilities-master-plan.jpg",
    "heroImageAlt": "Mixed-media collage of Overbrook High School’s facade with a vintage basketball, classroom blueprints, and Philadelphia street-map textures.",
